    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior features several minor dings, some noticeable paint fading on the hood and roof, and light surface scratches consistent with regular use. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some wear and minor staining on the carpets. Mechanically, it remains reliable and has been regularly serviced, though it may eventually require attention to standard wear-and-tear items like brake pads or tires. It is a solid, functional choice for someone prioritizing utility over aesthetics.",
      "price": 19200.0,
