    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously maintained since day one. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and no chips or scratches, while the interior remains in pristine state, still smelling like new with no signs of wear on the upholstery. Mechanically, it performs perfectly, with every feature functioning exactly as it did the day it left the factory. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer looking for a vehicle that is indistinguishable from a brand-new model.",
