    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable and well-maintained ride? This car is in great shape and ready for its next owner! It has been carefully looked after and runs beautifully, offering a smooth and comfortable driving experience. While you'll find some minor signs of normal wear and tear consistent with its age, it remains a solid, attractive vehicle that you can depend on for years to come. Come see why this well-cared-for car is such a fantastic value!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
